cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper proposes a regularization scheme for neural network classifiers, specifically ReLU networks, to improve their robustness. The paper focuses on machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI), as well as computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of adversarial attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR).
